      "abbreviation": "PX631301",
      "description": "This protocol includes 11 self-administered questions adapted from the Million Veteran Program (MVP) Baseline Survey (5 questions), MVP Lifestyle Survey (1 question), and the Mental Illness Research, Education, and Clinical Center (MIRECC) Demographics Form (5 questions).",
